Objective OSt-1C
Research attractiveness and internationalization
Promotion of inter-ministerial and inter-agency initiatives aimed at fostering the movement of talent not only at the European and international level, but also within national borders, with a systems approach and with a focus on the gender gap, countering phenomena that generate unfavorable or degrading environments

